
Open Ini
by Javier "Xaklse" Osset



Open Ini is a cross-desktop-platform editor for .ini files.
Right now it only opens text files and shows their content.


Uses the following libraries placed in:
...\Source\3rdp\Boost   (boost.org)
...\Source\3rdp\ImGui   (github.com/ocornut/imgui)
...\Source\3rdp\POCO    (pocoproject.org)
...\Source\3rdp\SFML    (sfml-dev.org)
...\Source\3rdp\TinyFD  (sourceforge.net/projects/tinyfiledialogs/files)


Application.cpp has the application entry point.


